      "447": {
        "class_type": "MarkdownNote",
        "widgets": {
          "text": "# 🎨 AI Image Generation Resolution Cheat Sheet (2025)\n\n## ✨ Absolute Sweet Spots for SDXL (use these 99% of the time)\n- **Portrait**: **832 × 1216** ← Current king\n- **Landscape**: **1216 × 832** ← Same but landscape\n- **Square**: **1024 × 1024** ← Perfect square, almost never fails\n- **Sharper alternative (portrait)**: **896 × 1152** ← New hidden gem (feels sharper)\n- **Sharper alternative (landscape)**: **1152 × 896**\n- **Cinematic/wide**: **1360 × 760** ← Amazing for wide shots\n\n## 🖼️ Best for Anime / Full-Body (SD 1.5 or Pony)\n- **Tall anime/full-body**: **768 × 1344** ← Best choice (may need hi-res fix)\n- **Wide anime/cinematic**: **1344 × 768**\n\n## 🔥 Flux.1 Resolutions (use these or you'll regret it)\n- **Safe square**: **1024 × 1024**\n- **Best quality right now**:\n  - Landscape: **1152 × 896**\n  - Portrait: **896 × 1152**\n- **Great wide/portrait**:\n  - Wide: **1360 × 1024**\n  - Portrait: **1024 × 1360**\n\n> **⚠️ Flux dev warning**: Avoid resolutions ending in 08 or 24 — it breaks the model!\n\n## 🕰️ Classic SD 1.5 / Pony / Animagine (still perfect in 2025)\n- **512 × 768** / **768 × 512**\n- **512 × 912** / **912 × 512** ← Tall waifu god-tier\n- **640 × 960** / **960 × 640**\n- **768 × 1344** ← Extreme tall (needs hi-res fix)\n\n## 🚀 Quick ComfyUI Cheat Sheet\n\n| Orientation      | Recommended Resolutions                  |\n|------------------|------------------------------------------|\n| **Portrait**     | 832×1216  or  **896×1152** (sharper)     |\n| **Landscape**    | 1216×832  or  **1152×896** (sharper)     |\n| **Square**       | **1024×1024**                            |\n| **Anime Tall**   | **768×1344**  or  **912×512**            |\n| **Flux Best**    | **1152×896** area (or swapped)           |\n\n## 💡 Pro Tips\n- For **Pony models**: CLIP skip **-2 is mandatory**.  \n  Use the **CLIP Set Last Layer** node — most reliable and works with every text encoder.\n\nCopy and paste this directly into a ComfyUI Markdown Note node for a clean, fancy-looking cheat sheet!"
        },
        "properties": {
          "ue_properties": {
            "widget_ue_connectable": {},
            "version": "7.5.2",
            "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
          }
        }
      },
