      "852": {
        "class_type": "PixaromaNote",
        "widgets": {
          "note_json": "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<p># 🎨 AI Image Generation Resolution Cheat Sheet (2025)</p><p><br></p><p>## ✨ Absolute Sweet Spots for SDXL (use these 99% of the time)</p><p>- **Portrait**: **832 × 1216** ← Current king</p><p>- **Landscape**: **1216 × 832** ← Same but landscape</p><p>- **Square**: **1024 × 1024** ← Perfect square, almost never fails</p><p>- **Sharper alternative (portrait)**: **896 × 1152** ← New hidden gem (feels sharper)</p><p>- **Sharper alternative (landscape)**: **1152 × 896**</p><p>- **Cinematic/wide**: **1360 × 760** ← Amazing for wide shots</p><p><br></p><p>## 🖼️ Best for Anime / Full-Body (SD 1.5 or Pony)</p><p>- **Tall anime/full-body**: **768 × 1344** ← Best choice (may need hi-res fix)</p><p>- **Wide anime/cinematic**: **1344 × 768**</p><p><br></p><p>## 🔥 Flux.1 Resolutions (use these or you'll regret it)</p><p>- **Safe square**: **1024 × 1024**</p><p>- **Best quality right now**:</p><p>&nbsp; - Landscape: **1152 × 896**</p><p>&nbsp; - Portrait: **896 × 1152**</p><p>- **Great wide/portrait**:</p><p>&nbsp; - Wide: **1360 × 1024**</p><p>&nbsp; - Portrait: **1024 × 1360**</p><p><br></p><p>&gt; **⚠️ Flux dev warning**: Avoid resolutions ending in 08 or 24 — it breaks the model!</p><p><br></p><p>## 🕰️ Classic SD 1.5 / Pony / Animagine (still perfect in 2025)</p><p>- **512 × 768** / **768 × 512**</p><p>- **512 × 912** / **912 × 512** ← Tall waifu god-tier</p><p>- **640 × 960** / **960 × 640**</p><p>- **768 × 1344** ← Extreme tall (needs hi-res fix)</p><p><br></p><p>## 🚀 Quick ComfyUI Cheat Sheet</p><p><br></p><p>| Orientation      | Recommended Resolutions                  |</p><p>|------------------|------------------------------------------|</p><p>| **Portrait**     | 832×1216  or  **896×1152** (sharper)     |</p><p>| **Landscape**    | 1216×832  or  **1152×896** (sharper)     |</p><p>| **Square**       | **1024×1024**                            |</p><p>| **Anime Tall**   | **768×1344**  or  **912×512**            |</p><p>| **Flux Best**    | **1152×896** area (or swapped)           |</p><p><br></p><p>## 💡 Pro Tips</p><p>- For **Pony models**: CLIP skip **-2 is mandatory**.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; Use the **CLIP Set Last Layer** node — most reliable and works with every text encoder.</p><p><br></p><p>Copy and paste this directly into a ComfyUI Markdown Note node for a clean, fancy-looking cheat sheet!</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":400,\"height\":200}",
          "note_dom": ""
        },
        "properties": {
          "aux_id": "ComfyUI-Pixaroma.git",
          "ver": "123685d8dd11526b41ce056affde32630e09fcbc",
          "Node name for S&R": "PixaromaNote",
          "ue_properties": {
            "widget_ue_connectable": {},
