      "854": {
        "class_type": "PixaromaNote",
        "widgets": {
          "note_json": "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<p>Orientation, Exact resolution (copy-paste), Ratio, Why it works perfectly</p><p>Vertical (portrait), 832 × 1216, 2:3, \\\"Gold standard – both girls head-to-toe, perfect for phone wallpaper style\\\"</p><p>Vertical (taller), 768 × 1344, 9:16, Extra height if one is riding/standing on the other</p><p>Vertical (safe max), 896 × 1280, 7:10, Maximum before hands/feet start breaking</p><p>Horizontal, 1216 × 832, 3:2, \\\"Side-by-side (e.g., both on all-fours, mirror shot)\\\"</p><p>Horizontal (wide), 1344 × 768, 16:9, \\\"Wide shot (both bent over a couch, etc.)\\\"</p><p>Square (last resort), 1024 × 1024, 1:1, Only if you absolutely must – one girl often gets cropped</p><p><br></p><p>Seed = 156</p><p><br></p><p>outdoors, sky, cloud, pov, building, scenery, lens flare, sunset, city, sun, cityscape, skyscraper, rooftop, city lights, sunrise</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>[NEW GIRL] 21 dec 2025</p><p>1girl, solo, long hair, breasts, looking at viewer, smile, bangs, large breasts, simple background, black hair, bare shoulders, jewelry, closed mouth, underwear, standing, panties, full body, pink hair, ass, multicolored hair, earrings, shoes, shiny, looking back, pants, dark skin, pink eyes, from behind, black footwear, shiny hair, two-tone hair, dark-skinned female, lips, gradient, shiny skin, gradient background, gradient hair, makeup, leaning forward, blue background, clothes pull, denim, sneakers, shiny clothes, sports bra, pants pull</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":300,\"height\":230}",
