      "868": {
        "class_type": "PixaromaNote",
        "widgets": {
          "note_json": "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h1># PROMPT EDITING — THE GOD MODE CHEAT SHEET&nbsp;&nbsp;</h1><h2>**2025 Final Edition — Memorize or Die Trying**</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 1. Golden Order (NEVER break this)</h3><h3><br></h3><h2>quality → subject → scene → style → extra</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>**Correct:**&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>`masterpiece, absurdres, perfect lighting, beautiful young goddess with silver hair, seductive pose, in luxury penthouse at night, cyberpunk neon lights, ultra-detailed background`</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 2. Weight Bible</h3><h2>| Weight   | Meaning                  |</h2><h2>|----------|--------------------------|</h2><h2>| 1.0      | Normal                   |</h2><h2>| 1.05–1.15| Gentle nudge             |</h2><h2>| 1.2–1.35 | **Sweet spot** (use 99% of the time) |</h2><h2>| 1.4+     | DOMINATES the image      |</h2><h2>| 0.8–0.9  | De-emphasize             |</h2><h2>| ≤0.7     | Barely exists            |</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 3. Nuclear Trick (Pony / Flux / SDXL)</h3><h2>Put **pose &amp; body** in **negative** with 1.2–1.4&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>→ Ends anatomy issues forever&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>Example negative:&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>`(seductive pose, from behind, kneeling:1.35)`</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 4. The BREAK God</h3><p><br></p><h2>quality, subject, style, BREAK pose, expression</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>→ Before BREAK = strong&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>→ After BREAK = ULTRA-strong</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 5. Parentheses Stacking (when you mean it)</h3><p><br></p><h2>((masterpiece)), (((perfect face))), ((((insanely detailed eyes))))</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>Use only when you're 100% serious.</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>## 6. The [text] De-emphasis Trick</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>[ugly], [deformed], [blurry:1.4], [low quality:1.6]</h2><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>## 7. AND Operator (Flux / SDXL / SD3)</h3><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><h3>## 8. The Magic Comma Rule</h3><h2>❌ Never: `beautiful girl with red hair wearing bikini`&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2><h2>✅ Always: `beautiful girl, red hair, wearing bikini`</h2><p><br></p><h3>## 9. Quality Stack 2025 (copy-paste this)</h3><p><br></p><p><br></p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":510,\"height\":840}",
          "note_dom": ""
        },
