      "894": {
        "class_type": "PixaromaNote",
        "widgets": {
          "note_json": "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<p><b>Absolutely! Below is a **detailed, tag-based Stable Diffusion prompt** optimized for maximum control — designed so you can easily **swap or modify tags** to customize pose, outfit, background, lighting, and style exactly how you want.</b></p><p><br></p><p>—</p><p><br></p><h2>## 🎯 FULL PROMPT (TAG-BASED FORMAT)</h2><p><br></p><p>```</p><p><b>(masterpiece, best quality, ultra-detailed, 8k, cinematic lighting, sharp focus, photorealistic anime hybrid, dynamic pose, dramatic angle)</b></p><p><br></p><p>[CHARACTER]:</p><p>black woman, dark brown skin, beautiful face, expressive almond eyes with long lashes, soft pink lips, curly afro hair with dreadlock twists, gold hoop earrings, subtle facial tattoos near temple and cheek, confident gaze</p><p><br></p><p>[OUTFIT]:</p><p>steampunk warrior armor, white corset top with gold buttons, brown leather shoulder pauldrons, black leather arm sleeves with brass rivets, high-waisted black shorts with thigh straps, red cape flowing behind, utility belt with pocket watch and glowing blue gem pendant, thigh garter strap with buckle</p><p><br></p><p>[POSE &amp; ACTION]:</p><p>standing on rooftop ledge, leaning slightly forward, one hand holding futuristic silver telescope near eye, other hand resting on knee, legs apart in powerful stance, looking directly at viewer with intense expression, wind blowing hair slightly</p><p><br></p><p>[BACKGROUND]:</p><p>urban cityscape background, tall beige buildings under hazy golden sunlight, distant skyscrapers, smoggy sky with fluffy clouds, industrial rooftops, gritty but romantic atmosphere</p><p><br></p><p>[STYLE &amp; RENDERING]:</p><p>digital painting, hyper-detailed skin texture, metallic sheen on armor, realistic fabric folds, volumetric lighting, rim light from sun, bokeh background blur, anime-inspired proportions with realistic shading, inspired by Final Fantasy + Cyberpunk + Afrofuturism</p><p><br></p><p>[COLOR PALETTE]:</p><p>warm golden hour tones, contrast of white/brown/black/red, metallic silver accents, glowing cyan gem highlights</p><p>```</p><p><br></p><p>—</p><p><br></p><h2>## 🔁 CUSTOMIZATION TAGS (SWAP THESE TO CHANGE YOUR IMAGE)</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>### 👤 Character Tags:</h2><h2>- `dark skin` → `light skin`, `olive skin`, `albino`</h2><h2>- `curly afro hair` → `braids`, `ponytail`, `buzz cut`, `long straight hair`</h2><h2>- `facial tattoos` → `no tattoos`, `cybernetic implants`, `glitter makeup`</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>### 👗 Outfit Tags:</h2><h2>- `steampunk warrior` → `cyberpunk hacker`, `space pirate`, `military commander`, `magical mage`</h2><h2>- `white corset` → `mesh top`, `bare chest`, `armored bikini`, `hooded robe`</h2><h2>- `red cape` → `black trench coat`, `no cape`, `floating energy aura`</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>### 🧍 Pose &amp; Action Tags:</h2><h2>- `leaning forward` → `sitting`, `kneeling`, `jumping`, `looking over shoulder`</h2><h2>- `holding telescope` → `holding gun`, `wielding sword`, `casting spell`, `drinking coffee`</h2><h2>- `confident gaze` → `smirking`, `serious`, `playful wink`, `teary-eyed`</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>### 🌆 Background Tags:</h2><h2>- `urban cityscape` → `desert wasteland`, `futuristic space station`, `jungle temple`, `underwater city`</h2><h2>- `golden hour` → `nighttime neon`, `stormy weather`, `rainy street`, `sunset glow`</h2><h2>- `hazy sky` → `clear blue sky`, `smoke-filled battlefield`, `aurora borealis`</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>### 🎨 Style &amp; Rendering Tags:</h2><h2>- `photorealistic anime hybrid` → `cel-shaded`, `oil painting`, `line art`, `3D render`</h2><h2>- `hyper-detailed skin` → `smooth cartoon skin`, `gritty texture`, `metallic skin`</h2><h2>- `Afrofuturism` → `gothic fantasy`, `sci-fi noir`, `post-apocalyptic`, `mythological`</h2><p><br></p><p>---</p><p><br></p><p>## 🚫 NEGATIVE PROMPT (ESSENTIAL FOR CLEAN OUTPUT):</p><p><br></p><p>```</p><p>lowres, blurry, pixelated, deformed hands, extra fingers, malformed face, ugly, text, watermark, signature, cartoonish, flat lighting, dull colors, overexposed, underexposed, low detail, bad anatomy, disfigured, mutated, extra limbs, cloned face, out of frame</p><p>```</p><p><br></p><p>---</p><p><br></p><p>## ⚙️ RECOMMENDED SETTINGS (for SDXL / Midjourney-style models):</p><p><br></p><p>- **Model:** `SDXL 1.0` or `Juggernaut XL`, `RealVisXL`, `AnimeV4`</p><p>- **Sampler:** DPM++ SDE Karras or Euler a</p><p>- **Steps:** 25–35</p><p>- **CFG Scale:** 7–9</p><p>- **Resolution:** 1024x1536 (portrait) or 768x1152 for speed</p><p>- **Seed:** Lock for consistency if desired</p><p><br></p><p>---</p><p><br></p><p>## 💡 TIP: Use “+” and “-” to boost or suppress elements:</p><p><br></p><p>Example:</p><p>&gt; `(steampunk armor:1.3), (gold accents:1.2), (blue gem:1.4), - (crowded background), - (casual pose)`</p><p><br></p><p>This lets you fine-tune what stands out — perfect for generating variations!</p><p><br></p><p>—</p><p><br></p><p>Let me know if you want this prompt adapted for **specific poses** (e.g., action shot, sitting, back view), **different genres** (fantasy, cyberpunk, historical), or even **full body vs close-up** — I’ll build it for you tag-by-tag. ✨</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":400,\"height\":200}",
          "note_dom": ""
        },
